Suaminya, Farid, cuba membantu namun keadaan menjadi semakin buruk apabila rahsia lama yang disembunyikan mula terbongkar bahawa roh janin itu menuntut keadilan atas dosa masa lalu mereka.

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Aafiyah dan Rizq anak kepada pasangan Adelia dan Rafeeq. Aafiyah dimasukkan ke hospital, semasa abangnya menzirahi Aafiyah doktor mengesahkan gadis tersebut mengalami trauma dan lupa ingatan. Sebulan sebelum kejadian, Aafiyah menyambut harijadinya di sebuah hotel tempat ibunya bekerja. Disebabkan kesibukan bekerja, kedua-duanya meninggalkan Aafiyah keseorangan. Aafiyah ternampak seorang bertopeng membunuh seorang wanita, dia yang ketakutan cuba melarikan diri tetapi berjaya ditangkap oleh pembunuh tersebut. Aafiyah berjanji tidak akan membuka rahsia tersebut kepada sesiapa. Aafiyah bersama ibunya berjaya menyelamatkan berkereta keluar dari hotel. Namun pembunuh tersebut berjaya menahan mereka dan membunuh ibunya

programme.title: Kutuk
programme.desc: Maya, seorang jururawat yang baru berpindah ke sebuah asrama lama di pinggir bandar, mula diganggu oleh kejadian aneh dan menyeramkan. Dia kemudian menyedari bahawa asrama itu menyimpan rahsia gelap tentang sumpahan yang menghantui setiap penghuni yang tinggal di situ. Untuk menyelamatkan diri, Maya perlu membongkar misteri di sebalik kutukan tersebut sebelum terlambat.

programme.title: Barajiwa S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Apabila Uzair pulang ke rumah untuk bersama adik dan ibunya, dia dihalau oleh ibunya yang tidak mahu dia tinggal bersama mereka. Uzair mendapattahu bahawa Ashikin telah disimpan oleh Imran dan dia pergi untuk menyelamatkannya. Apabila Ashikin menyuruh melupakannya, Uzair kecewa dan pergi ke bandar.

programme.title: Parole Examiner Lee EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Lee Han-shin memulakan tugas baharunya sebagai pemeriksa pembebasan bersyarat dan mendapati sistem itu dipengaruhi oleh kuasa serta wang. Dalam masa yang sama, detektif Ahn Seo-yoon menyiasat kes pembunuhan yang berkait dengan keluarga chaebol Ojung Group.

programme.title: Parole Examiner Lee EP2 S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Han-shin menimbulkan kemarahan pihak berkuasa apabila menolak permohonan pembebasan seorang tokoh berpengaruh. Seo-yoon menemui petunjuk yang menghubungkan kesnya dengan seorang banduan yang sedang menunggu parol.

programme.title: Transporter 3
programme.desc: Frank Martin terpaksa menghantar Valentina, anak perempuan pegawai kerajaan Ukraine yang diculik, dari Marseilles ke Odessa melalui Laut Hitam. Dalam perjalanan, dia terpaksa bersemuka dengan samseng yang ingin menggagalkan penghantaran tersebut

programme.title: Tujuh
programme.desc: Sekumpulan tujuh sahabat yang pernah terlibat dalam satu kejadian tragis bertahun lalu kembali dihantui apabila seorang demi seorang mula mati secara misteri. Dalam usaha mencari kebenaran, mereka mula menyedari bahawa dosa silam mereka tidak akan terampun dan pembalasan sedang menanti.

programme.title: Ceroboh
programme.desc: Selepas dunia dilanda makhluk asing yang dikenali sebagai Penunggu Langityang mampu mengawal minda manusiaenam rakan berlindung di sebuah bangunan usang. Namun apabila salah seorang daripada mereka terdedah kepada mereka, rasa curiga dan paranoia mula menjangkiti kumpulan itu, membawa ancaman yang lebih membahayakan daripada serangan di luar.

programme.title: Skrip 7707
programme.desc: Sebuah filem antologi seram yang menghimpunkan beberapa kisah menakutkan berasaskan skrip misteri bernombor 7707. Setiap kisah menyingkap rahsia gelap yang penuh dendam, roh, dan balasan.

programme.title: The House
programme.desc: Selepas memutuskan untuk tinggal sementara di vila kampung halaman mereka sambil menantikan kelahiran bayi pertama, pasangan Junui dan Biroo menghadapi gangguan yang bukan sahaja melibatkan kenangan silam tetapi juga kehadiran misteri di rumah yang mereka duduki. Junui mula terganggu oleh bayangan cinta lamanya, Jihhee, yang hilang di vila itu, manakala Biroo melihat jejak-jejak asing dan merasa seperti sentiasa diawasi.

programme.title: Parole Examiner Lee EP3 S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Han-shin mengesyaki wujud rangkaian rasuah dalam sistem parol. Seo-yoon pula mendapati ada banduan dijadikan kambing hitam untuk jenayah besar. Hwa-ran muncul menawarkan maklumat tentang Ojung Group.

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Barajiwa EP6 S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Noramina kagum dengan kemahiran bertarung Uzair dan menawar pekerjaan sebagai pengawal peribadinya. Uzair kini mempunyai pekerjaan yang sesuai dan boleh menyewa tempat tinggal sendiri. Hatta mula sedar ada sesuatu yang baik dan istimewa pada Uzair. Uzair mula mesra dengan Noramina.

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Aafiyah dan Rizq anak kepada pasangan Adelia dan Rafeeq. programme.title: Shut In
programme.desc: Seorang psikolog kanak-kanak yang menjadi janda menjalani kehidupan terpencil di kawasan luar bandar New England. Terkandas dalam ribut salji yang mematikan, dia mesti mencari cara untuk menyelamatkan seorang budak lelaki sebelum dia hilang selamanya.

programme.title: Arjuna S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Arjuna cuba difitnah melakukan perkara sumbang oleh Amutra dan kawan-kawannya. Mereka ingin membawa Arjuna menghadap ke pengadilan tetapi berlaku pergelutan, di mana Jagat iaitu sepupu kepada Amutra tidak sengaja menikam Amutra kemudian melarikan diri.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Dendang Remaja
programme.desc: Di sebuah akademi seni, terdapat dua kumpulan pelajar yang berseteru. Mereka tidak serius ketika belajar dan lebih menggemari muzik dari barat. Oleh kerana tidak mendapat bimbingan yang sewajarnya, para pelajar ini menjadi semakin liar sehingga menganggu ketenteraman.

programme.title: Awang Spanar
programme.desc: Awang Spanar, gelaran yang diberi kerana kemahirannya yang pandai membaiki bot melalui pelbagai liku kehidupan bersama rakannya, Salleh. Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. Menjadi buruan mafia, mereka meminta bantuan seorang detektif, Lydia.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Marah-Marah Sayang
programme.desc: Tiga jejaka yang cintakan muzik terpaksa dilepaskan dari kerja masing-masing kerana asyik leka dibuai irama ketika sedang bekerja yang menyebabkan ketidakselesaan orang lain. Rostam, Roslan dan Rosdin mula jatuh cinta terhadap tiga anak dara yang cantik namun Salina, Sarina dan Satina menolak cinta mereka. Pelbagai usaha telah dilakukan oleh mereka dan akhirnya mereka berjaya mengahwini gadis-gadis pilihan mereka itu. Syarat-syarat telah diberi jika ingin berkahwin namun telah dilanggar, ini telah mengakibatkan perkahwinan mereka menjadi kucar-kacir.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bernama Os bekerja sebagai budak pejabat di sebuah syarikat insurans di ibu kota. Pada suatu hari berlaku satu kehilangan berlian di sebuah acara pameran. Os cuba menyelesaikan kes kehilangan berlian itu dengan bantuan seekor monyet yang menjadi sahabatnya.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

programme.title: Tak Kisahlah Beb
programme.desc: Bob, seorang DJ di sebuah kelab malam terkenal dengan sikapnya yang suka mementikngkan diri sendiri selain perangainya yang nakal. Diperangkapnya Rozi, lalu Bob menodai dan meninggalkannya. Pertengkaran berlaku apabila mereka bertemu kembali atas apa yang Bob telah lakukan kepadanya. Setelah disedarkan rakan-rakannya, Bob menyesali tindakannya dan cuba untuk mencari jalan berbaik semula.

programme.desc: Bob, seorang DJ di sebuah kelab malam terkenal dengan sikapnya yang suka mementikngkan diri sendiri selain perangainya yang nakal. Diperangkapnya Rozi, lalu Bob menodai dan meninggalkannya. Pertengkaran berlaku apabila mereka bertemu kembali atas apa yang Bob telah lakukan kepadanya. Setelah disedarkan rakan-rakannya, Bob menyesali tindakannya dan cuba untuk mencari jalan berbaik semula.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bernama Os bekerja sebagai budak pejabat di sebuah syarikat insurans di ibu kota. Pada suatu hari berlaku satu kehilangan berlian di sebuah acara pameran. Os cuba menyelesaikan kes kehilangan berlian itu dengan bantuan seekor monyet yang menjadi sahabatnya.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Awang Spanar
programme.desc: Awang Spanar, gelaran yang diberi kerana kemahirannya yang pandai membaiki bot melalui pelbagai liku kehidupan bersama rakannya, Salleh. Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. Menjadi buruan mafia, mereka meminta bantuan seorang detektif, Lydia.

Sementara itu, WAWA dan BOBBY menjalani kehidupan yang sederhana dan menghadapi masalah kewangan. WAWA mula marah kepada BOBBY kerana mereka tidak mempunyai cukup wang semasa tempoh kehamilannya dan menjelang kelahiran. Sebagai seorang kawan yang baik, ADNAN meminjamkan wang kepada BOBBY. Namun, BOBBY tidak lagi berani meminta wang daripada ADNAN selepas dimarahi olehnya yang tertekan dengan keadaan NADIA. Akibat desakan hidup, BOBBY membuat keputusan untuk berlumba semula.

programme.title: Nada Siar S1 Ep65
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 2
programme.desc: Adnan, seorang penunggang motosikal jalanan yatim piatu yang dijaga oleh ibu saudaranya. Sebaliknya, Nadia dilahirkan dalam keluarga kaya dan kini memiliki pekerjaan yang stabil. Kedua-dua insan yang berbeza ini bertemu secara kebetulan dan akhirnya menjalin hubungan. Kini, dalam "Adnan Sempit 2", Shaheizy Sam kembali memegang watak sebagai Adnan, mengisahkan cabaran dan dugaan dalam kehidupannya serta hubungannya dengan Nadia.

programme.title: Longkai
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang geng 'longkai' (tonto atau penunda kereta). Eddie dan Bada ialah adik-beradik longkai yang terkenal. Semua kenderaan yang ditunda oleh mereka akan dibawa ke bengkel Rimau. Walaupun dia seorang wanita, Rimau berperwatakan sedikit tomboy dan lasak. Rimau telah jatuh cinta dengan Bada, tetapi dia tidak pernah berani untuk meluahkan perasaannya walaupun dia nampak 'tough'.

programme.title: Gila Gila Remaja 2
programme.desc: Filem ni adalah sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Remaja (1985). Ia bawa vibe remaja moden dengan konflik cinta, persahabatan, dan cabaran zaman baru. Kisahnya lebih fokus pada hidup remaja kolej & sekolah memandu, dengan isu sosial yang dekat dengan golongan muda persaingan, cinta segitiga, serta impian masing-masing.

programme.title: Jhangri
programme.desc: Jhangri ialah filem komedi romantik aksi penuh dengan suspens, kejutan dan plot twist. Ia mengisahkan perjalanan Vikran yang cuba menawan hati Jaanu, gadis yang sepatutnya dijodohkan dengannya tetapi menolak tanpa sebab jelas. Apabila rahsia penolakan itu terbongkar, kisah bertukar daripada romantik komedi kepada aksi suspens

programme.title: Geran
programme.desc: Ali dan Fatimah berasa kecewa dengan adik mereka, Mat Arip, apabila dia gagal pulang dengan geran tanah pusaka mereka. Ali perlu mencari Mat Arip, yang telah bergaul dengan kumpulan yang salah dan terlibat dalam perjudian serta perlumbaan haram, lalu membawanya pulang kepada bapa mereka, Pak Nayan.

programme.title: Hantu Dalam Botol Kicap
programme.desc: Tiga kanak-kanak yang jahil melanggar peraturan di rumah nenek mereka, menyebabkan meraka terlepas bebas.

programme.title: Melawan Takdir
programme.desc: Filem ni kisahkan perjalanan hidup Quraisy Mathar sendiri (pengarah filem ni). Ia mengangkat pengalaman hidupnya yang penuh cabaran sejak kecil kehilangan orang tersayang, jatuh bangun dalam hidup, sampai berjaya jadi seorang sineas. Cerita ni tunjuk bagaimana semangat, doa, dan keyakinan boleh buat seseorang bangkit walaupun diuji dengan pelbagai takdir yang pahit.

programme.title: Salina
programme.desc: Salina tinggal di sebuah banglo cantik yang mempunyai sejarah misteri. Apabila kejadian aneh dan menakutkan mula berlaku, terutamanya terhadap anak-anaknya, Salina mula menyiasat sejarah banglo itu untuk melindungi mereka. Namun, keadaan menjadi semakin teruk sehingga membawa kepada kematian yang tidak dijangka.

Namun, ketika ibunya jatuh sakit, Bayu mula menyedari kasih sayang dan pengorbanan besar seorang ibu serta pentingnya taat dan berbakti kepadanya.

programme.title: Mereka Yang Pergi S1 Ep22
programme.desc: Mengungkap kisah-kisah menyentuh hati di sekeliling kita, tentang mereka yang kehilangan insan tersayang. Mampukah mereka kembali dalam kehangatan keluarga?

programme.title: Ngga Usah Ngadi Ngadi Nanti Kamu Jatuh Hati
programme.desc: Derry memutuskan hubungan cintanya dengan Vina kerana mereka terlibat dalam pertengkaran dan salah faham. Derry yang kini semakin rapat dengan Elsa, membantu Elsa yang sedang menjual jagung bakar. Papa Derry yang mengetahui hal tersebut marah kepada Derry dan melarang Derry untuk mendekati Elsa lagi. Dia lebih setuju jika Derry bersama Vina. Menurut papa Derry, imej hotel akan menjadi buruk jika Derry terus bersama Elsa dan membantu Elsa menjual jagung bakar.

programme.title: D'Academy 7 S7 Ep57
programme.desc: D' Academy 7 ialah musim ketujuh rancangan nyanyian popular Indonesia yang fokus pada muzik dangdut. Peserta dari seluruh negara bertanding dengan menyanyikan lagu dangdut, menunjukkan bakat vokal dan persembahan mereka. Sepanjang musim, mereka dinilai oleh juri profesional dan undian penonton. Siapakah yang akan menjuarai D'Academy musim ketujuh?

programme.title: My Heart S1 Ep82
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Batam Bumi Segantang Lada S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Sebuah semi-dokumentari yang meneroka Batam, bandar perindustrian baharu dan hab pengangkutan yang pesat membangun di Indonesia.

programme.title: Bidadari Surgamu S1 Ep464
programme.desc: Menceritakan kisah seorang gadis bernama Sakinah yang menjalani kehidupan penuh tekanan akibat fitnah dan dipaksa untuk berkahwin dengan seseorang yang tidak mencintainya. Tidak hanya itu, Sakinah juga dihalang untuk mengetahui siapa ibu kandungnya yang tega membuangnya.

programme.title: Tukar Nasib Kok Jadi Makin Asik
programme.desc: Nila dan Fira adalah adik-beradik. Sifat Nila dan Fira sangatlah berbeza. Nila adalah seorang gadis cantik dan bergaya, dan Nila juga disukai oleh ramai lelaki di sekolahnya. Berbeza dengan Fira yang tampil sederhana dan biasa. Namun, Fira adalah seorang chef di sebuah restoran. Pada suatu ketika, Fira dan Nila terlibat pertengkaran di dalam kereta, dan akhirnya kereta yang mereka naiki melanggar pokok. Nila dan Fira dimasukkan ke hospital, dan nampaknya tubuh mereka telah tertukar.

Suatu hari, ketika dia sedang menyanyi di tepi jalan, pegawai penguat kuasa datang untuk menangkapnya dan memaksa Rosa melarikan diri dengan tergesa-gesa. Dalam kekalutan itu, Rosa secara tidak sengaja mengambil lori milik Attar. Untuk mengelak daripada terus diburu, Rosa meminta Attar mengambilnya bekerja sebagai penyanyi di kedai makanan laut miliknya. Lama-kelamaan, hubungan mereka semakin rapat dan perasaan cinta mula berputik. Namun, kisah cinta mereka diuji apabila muncul bekas kekasih Rosa yang bakal berkahwin.

However, he also respects their individual passions and aspirations. Because of their fathers dream of innovation, the lives of the Chao brothers are about to change.

programme.title: New Taiwan Go S1 Ep3300
programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside.

programme.title: Stylish Man-The Chef S1 Ep4127
programme.desc: Stylish Man The Chef is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng and Genie Chuo, together with professional chef, James. There are two main themes for the program, which are Big Stars Come to Cook and Five-Star Cooking Show. Stylish Man The Chef containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa S1 Ep305
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Hot Door Night S1 Ep2427
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: The Sound of Happiness S1 Ep191
programme.desc: Wu is a senior police officer has always wanted a son to carry his family name and join the force. However, he and wife are bequeathed with four daughters! As a doting father, his chief objective is to help them find happiness in their marriages. In this charming drama, Wu & his wife become their daughters greatest haven, through the ups and downs they face as married women.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan S1 Ep5231
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover to a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Way We Talk, The
programme.desc: This is a soul-searching story about three youths: Wolf, Sophie and Alan, each living with a different form of deafness. Through sign language, they cultivate a profound friendship and offer each other unwavering support. United by love and friendship, the trio embarks on a journey of self-discovery and resilience.

programme.title: Customs Frontline
programme.desc: After boarding an unauthorized cargo ship and finding its entire crew dead, the Hong Kong Customs officers uncover a hidden cache of illegal weapons linked to an international conflict. As Customs officer Zhou Zheng Li and Interpol's Ying go undercover, they unveil a multinational operation with ties closer to home.

programme.title: The Hedgehog
programme.desc: Wang's odd behaviour and quirky ideas make him a social outcast. His teenage nephew Zhou, who is ashamed of his stutter, becomes Wang's only friend. Together, these misfits challenge traditional family expectations and social misunderstandings, supporting and inspiring each other as they seek their own paths in life.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: There Is No Escape From Fate
programme.desc: Hong Kong businessman Yu and his secretary travel abroad for business meetings. When the secretary is killed in their hotel, Yu is arrested. Despite pleading not guilty, Yu is imprisoned in a cruel multinational prison where the warden enjoys torturing prisoners, and he must find a way to escape from this dark and deadly prison to survive.

programme.title: MuMu
programme.desc: Mumu, a cheerful seven-year-old girl, lives with her deaf father in a deaf community and connects him to the outside world. However, their peaceful life is disrupted when her estranged mother reappears, pushing Mumu into the hearing world. Meanwhile, her father becomes ensnared by a gang that exploits the deaf to commit crimes.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kong's grassroots performing artists as they fight against the government's plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Liu's family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: A Legend
programme.desc: Archaeologist Professor Fang uncovers artifacts from a glacier expedition that resembles a jade pendant in his dream. To unveil the truth, Professor Fang leads his team to a journey into the glacier, embarking on a fantastical adventure together.

programme.title: Table for Six 2
programme.desc: The sequel to "Table for Six", Bernard and Lung plan to get married while their eldest brother is away. Yet, the weddings spiral into a chaotic battleground with escalating family drama, creating a messy affair for everyone involved.

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: The Monkey King
programme.desc: After Goddess Nuwa sacrifices herself to save the mortal world, Monkey King comes into being from one of her crystals. Powerful and uncontrollable, Monkey King challenges the Jade Emperor and causes an uproar in heaven, unwittingly creating an opportunity for the wicked Buffalo Demon King to wage war in heaven.

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firm's VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: May We Chat
programme.desc: Yan, Wei Wei and Yi Ji are three troubled young women from very different backgrounds who met on We Chat, a social media platform, and will do anything to escape each of their troubled lives. When Yan suddenly disappears one day, Wei Wei and Yi Ji start to track her whereabouts, only to find out shocking truths about her that were never revealed.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Phua Chu Kang: The Movie
programme.desc: Ah Ma visits Phua Chu Kang, who is now based in Malaysia, but soon goes missing. Phua desperately searches for Ah Ma and finds her in a nursing home run by Lim Lau Pek, who unexpectedly offers Phua a renovation job. When suspicious deaths start occurring in the nursing home, Lim becomes the prime suspect. How will Phua resolve this?

programme.title: S Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk witnesses a suspect's murder while investigating an illegal soccer gambling case, but is unable to disclose information to Chief Inspector Lau due to his code of confidentiality, thereby hindering Lau's investigation. While starting the case with mutual distrust, they end up reaching a rapport to uproot the crime syndicate.

programme.title: Way We Talk, The
programme.desc: This is a soul-searching story about three youths: Wolf, Sophie and Alan, each living with a different form of deafness. Through sign language, they cultivate a profound friendship and offer each other unwavering support. United by love and friendship, the trio embarks on a journey of self-discovery and resilience.

programme.title: Kungfu Stuntmen
programme.desc: Hong Kong action cinema is famous for its real kung fu moves performed by a group called Kung Fu Stuntmen. This docu-film pays tribute to the generations of kung fu stuntmen, with the crew spending over two years digging archives and interviewing many talents, including the most prominent masters like Jackie Chan, Donnie Yen and Sammo Hung.

programme.title: Cesium Fallout
programme.desc: A massive fire caused by illegal garbage smuggling has triggered a radiation crisis in Hong Kong. Government advisor Simon joins the crisis response team led by Acting Chief Executive to avert the disaster. A fire brigade is tasked to enter the radiation zone and stop the cesium fallout. Facing the unprecedented catastrophe, can they save the city?

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: This tale of a honorable fighter's retraining in the "Iron Palm" style, that became the first international martial arts movie hit and made a continent-spanning star of Lo Lieh.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rong's hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sister's wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman. After the marriage mismatches are revealed, the lovers and their families are taken to court, where Prefecture Chief Qiao manages to work out a happy ending.

programme.title: Angel with the Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller, playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts World's intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servant's confusion, threatening the couple's union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Shaolin Temple
programme.desc: As more people are learning martial arts from Shaolin, the Qing court orders for it to be banned and plans to destroy the temple. The Shaolin disciples decide to take their protest to the streets, using Shaolin skills to curb their hatred, but when the Qing troops start attacking Shaolin Temple, the disciples vow to protect it at all costs.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his people's livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Constable Wen Chao Fan and his father are framed for a jewel robbery they did not commit. On the run from the law and becoming a wanted fugitive, Wen must recover the jewels in order to clear his family name, but unfortunately he is not the only one seeking the stolen jewels...

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: Adapted from the classic Chinese novel of the same title, the story follows Monk Tang San Zang's journey to the West in search of the Buddhist Sutra. On the way, he encounters and takes as disciples, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing.

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: The Black Falcon
programme.desc: Jenny Hu and veteran co-star Margaret Tu Chuan join longtime0020idol Paul Chang Chung in a battle against the notorious Black Falcon crime mob in Singapore. Together they have to face forgery, fire, and even poisoned needles to stop the mob.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a man's role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content, yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: Four Riders
programme.desc: Four martial arts experts live in Seoul after the Korean War in the 1950s. One of them inexplicably crosses path with a drug trafficking syndicate, and his three friends have no choice but to fight a brutal battle on his side...

programme.title: Martial Arts of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers' death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: Swordsman and Enchantress
programme.desc: The story happens in a martial arts world where everyone tries to obtain the "Deer Sword". Lian's wife is wounded in an ambush and his rival Xiao saves her. They escape to Xiao's home and he treats her poisonous wound. This leads Lian to suspect his wife's faithfulness and results in several blood-splattering duels with Xiao.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Long's wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: Li Xun Huan is a sentimental swordsman who has lived peacefully outside the martial arts world for the past ten years. He returns home after knowing that the Plum Blossom Bandit is back to his old tricks, only to find that everything has changed.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yu's beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: The Black Enforcer
programme.desc: Lung the Black Enforcer is ordered to escort a murderer Fei to prison. While taking shelter in Lung's house from the snowstorm, Fei is rescued by his gang and Fei kills Lung's mother and sister before escaping. Lung is imprisoned for the failed task and after being released, he vows to avenge his family by killing Fei.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: Honey Bunny In Treasure Hunt S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Honey, Bunny and their friends team up to help a man whose treasure was stolen by two thieves.

programme.title: Prince Jai Aur Dumdaar Viru S1 Ep24
programme.desc: A prince and a commoner who are best friends keep having to thwart the plots of the prince's scheming, ambitious minister.

programme.title: Prince Jai Aur Dumdaar Viru S1 Ep25
programme.desc: A prince and a commoner who are best friends keep having to thwart the plots of the prince's scheming, ambitious minister.

programme.title: Sab Jholmaal Hai S1 Ep57
programme.desc: A hilarious animal chase comedy about the secret life and adventures of a dog, a parrot and twin bobcats living with Ms Katkar.

programme.title: Sab Jholmaal Hai S1 Ep58
programme.desc: A hilarious animal chase comedy about the secret life and adventures of a dog, a parrot and twin bobcats living with Ms Katkar.
